KAhm wrote:<BR>
<DIV></DIV><BR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
Frodlin wrote:<BR>
<DIV></DIV><BR>
<P>I certainly don't think that pulling is "survival", it's crowd control, it's an ability.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I most certainly DO think that self healing is survival and that self healing and raw mitigation should be balanced with one another to acheive a level of parity, and that solo and pvp play MUST be factored as part of the overall balance equation, and that it's a darned shame that they've been ignored for so long.<BR></P><BR>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><EM>It's hard to compare Solo and PvP to Grouping because there is a fundamental change in dynamics, they make poor group models.</EM> </P>
<P>Sure, but they should still be balanced.&nbsp;&nbsp; Solo and PvP should be as balanced as grouping is, otherwise there really isn't any balance.</P>
<P>I'm not desiring to compare them, only to say that they should also be balanced on their own.</P></BLOCKQUOTE><BR>
